Before changing anything in this repository, read and follow `MILEPILOT_MANIFESTO.md`.

That file defines:

- Why MilePilot exists and who it serves
- Mission, design, and development philosophy
- Product principles and tone of voice
- The golden rule for every release
- The required development order for all work

Apply the manifesto to every decision: features, UI, copy, architecture, and commits.
